I think this PR needs a couple of revisions but its a good start. 

My biggest question is about depending on python-bidi. It does not look like it is actively maintained. Are there alternatives? How much trouble is it to implement ourselves? 

@pombredanne, I noticed you use it [here](https://github.com/pombredanne/ts-graph/blob/743a66219ec1bf529ba0fed3afa3bb432ef93fe8/node_attrs/python-bidi.json). What do you think about adding python-bidi as a dependency?

